OL,3,CFootball fan banned for 'horrendous'
OL,4,Cracism towards Blackburn star
OL,6,FA man has been given a three-year
OL,7,Ffootball banning order after racially
OL,8,Fabusing a Blackburn Rovers player
OL,9,Fduring the East Lancashire Derby.
OL,11,FDuring the 1-1 draw at Turf Moor, Neil
OL,12,FJeffrey, 61, shouted a "horrendous"
OL,13,Fracist slur at Blackburn Rovers
OL,14,Fstriker Makhtar Gueye who had just
OL,15,Fbeen given a red card.
OL,17,FThe incident, which happened in the
OL,18,FJimmy McIlroy Stand in August 2024,
OL,19,Fwas reported to Burnley Football Club,
OL,20,Fwho informed Lancashire Police.
