OL,3,CFootball fan banned for 'horrendous'
OL,4,Cracism towards Blackburn star
OL,6,FJeffrey of Roe Greave Road,
OL,7,FOswaldtwistle, was interviewed on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of Racially Aggravated
OL,9,FPublic Order. He fully admitted the
OL,10,Foffence, and pleaded guilty at
OL,11,FBlackburn Magistrates Court.
OL,13,FAs well as being given the football
OL,14,Fbanning order, Jeffrey was fined #400,
OL,15,Fordered to pay prosecution costs of
OL,16,F#85 and a victim surcharge of #160.
