OL,3,CFootball fan banned for 'horrendous'
OL,4,Cracism towards Blackburn star
OL,6,FPC Byron Worrall, of Lancashire
OL,7,FPolice, said: "Behaviour of this
OL,8,Fnature has no place in society and
OL,9,Fwill not be tolerated by Lancashire
OL,10,FPolice, Blackburn Rovers and Burnley
OL,11,Ffootball clubs or the courts.
OL,13,F"If you do decide to behave in this
OL,14,Fabhorrent way, Lancashire Police will
OL,15,Fwork with Blackburn Rovers and Burnley
OL,16,Ffootball clubs to identify you and put
OL,17,Fyou before the courts."
