OL,6,FA Burnley Football Club spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "Burnley Football Club has a
OL,8,Fzero-tolerance policy regarding
OL,9,Fdiscrimination of any sort and will
OL,10,Fcontinue to enforce and support all
OL,11,Fefforts to eradicate this kind of
OL,12,Fbehaviour.
OL,14,F"The club moved swiftly to assist in
OL,15,Fidentifying the individual and stand
OL,16,Ftogether with the police and football
OL,17,Fauthorities to make matches a safer
OL,18,Fplace for all supporters."
